Utilities to analyze data sets.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Profiler
    Analyzes data sets.
    Profiler.Statistic
    Statistic produced by the profiler.
  • Class Summary

    Profiler.Column
    Column.
    Profiler.Distribution
    Value distribution, including cardinality and optionally values, of a column or set of columns.
